dct_title_s: The Rand-McNally new library atlas map of Turkey in Europe, Roumania, Servia, Bulgaria, and Montenegro
dct_description_sm: Running title in margin: Library atlas of the world. [Turkey in Europe.]. 71-72. Map of Turkey and the Balkan Peninsula; relief shown by hachures. Inset: Crete or Candia. From: The library atlas of the world. Chicago, New York : Rand McNally & Co., c1912.
